<br>
<br>
For how many centuries have I been your devoted follower and commander of the children of the Eternal Night.  How long the Sinchyld of today and those before us answered to your beck and call. How long my lords? Perhaps too long. Perhaps so long, that you have forgotten all that we have done in the name of the Eternal Night. Perhaps you have mistaken me for one of your lowly dogs for far too long. Perhaps it is time for your reign to end.<br>
<br>
I will not step down as commander of the vampyre nation of the coterie. I will not hand over to you my children, and I will naut hand to you my title as king of the Night Wings.<br>
What I will give to you is notice.<br>
<br>
That I am coming for you. <br>
<br>
There will be change.<br>
<br>
Out of respect I have allowed you both to sit high upon the council, when we know it is my noble blood that should rule the legions.  The time for my rule is at hand.<br>
<br>
The time for your eternal rest is now.<br>
<br>
Ready your forces all you wish…<br>
<br>
Arm yourselves with the greatest weapons ever created by the gods themselves….<br>
<br>
But most of all prepare for a new era …<br>
<br>
The king is coming for his crown.<br>
<br>
Ky'lek Dominion Sinchyld.<br>
